data.description: Settle down on acreage in this quiet and convenient spot just outside of Hixton. Super cute 3 bed 2.5 bath farmhouse. Kitchen has vaulted ceiling and beams with skylight for tons of natural light. Huge back porch is the perfect pantry. Living room has a wood stove that really throws off the heat. Main floor has large master bedroom, full bath. Secondary bedroom has a 3/4 bath ensuite. Third bedroom is 2nd story with tons of closet space. Oversized 2 car garage even has a heated and insulated attached workshop for all your hobbies or business needs. Lean to and chicken coop are bonuses! Land is beautiful, open and rolling, great privacy on a paved road. Come to the country!
